{"tid":1475780,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"到底點先叫做義士? 同我入黎睇下點樣先對得住個義字","createTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T15:37:45.000Z","uid":19817,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7a84ca2ed737188f854a53d110345cb9e0a86fd8","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAVA8uj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAVA8uj.jpg&h=556a6021&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n借用另一個POST既圖<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地擔住個義字, 就要貫徹始終, 永遠要記住自己初衷, 唔好背道而馳</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n一個義字所承擔既野的確係好重, 的確係好多拘束, 唔可以盡情發洩不滿<br />\n<br />\n但大家一定要記住我地做既野係有底線,有限制<br />\n<br />\n我亦相信71逃亡台灣既義士, 同埋以死明志既烈士都唔希望我地忘記左個義字<br />\n<br />\n正因為我地係有義, 有底線, 有限制先可以凝聚到咁多民意, 運動先可以持續咁耐<br />\n<br />\n我地適當既時間可以武制暴 但要光明正大, 犯我者必誅! <br />\n<br />\n文宣組可以有小聰明, 但唔可以破左道德既底線<br />\n<br />\n政府一路做緊既野就係同我地鬥搶道德高地, 去污名化我地<br />\n<br />\n政府不斷用流氓用下三流手段去對待我地就係想我地失去理性<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想我地其中有人由天使同騎士墜落成惡魔, 學左共產黨果套做事方式, 呢條係不歸路黎</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n記得有咩事, 和理非一定要拍片<br />\n<br />\n勇武既點到即止, 自衛為主<br />\n<br />\n至於你話底線係邊, 我認為當大部分係都係E同F既時候, 大家個底線只能去到C<br />\n<br />\n而且AB級到底算唔算義士? 做左既話後果會如何好難想像, 大家真係唔好俾憤怒掩蓋雙眼<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山, 但唔代表爬到見唔到大家既影子, 始終都要齊上齊落, 大家要明白呢個道理<br />\n<br />\n當然我都好希望所有F既人可以練功升哂上E<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  豬隊友們我地會等你"},{"pid":"f7880acc194c3589a9e32a4a159948a7b4fcf6f4","tid":1475780,"uid":268213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:59:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvJyVf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvJyVf2.jpg&h=f574c200&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/exRkAf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FexRkAf3.jpg&h=4bc1efb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2b8dee3de90907a4aebd48a8c75986153240d14","tid":1475780,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正經post冇人推！？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">Set deadline再升級係大多手足嘅共識 大家一齊去公投同討下啦 要過5,000正評 民間記者會應該要反映到抗爭者主流意見同策略</span> </span><br />\n冇網絡大軍同P牌不能好評 要靠大家！！<br />\n<br />\n【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dEHHFS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dEHHFS</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"1794920d0f22d04948d4616014fc80c5709bc9c6","tid":1475780,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:01:12.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d6b88e87bd5927751aeb707e12fecc9e750aae5a","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da0a49ddce35a4b3813f0ae38ea137dd7ad38e6","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:06:05.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"9d8b406dc554ee540fb0b431ce04bc29c0b72a57","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地擔住個義字, 就要貫徹始終, 永遠要記住自己初衷, 唔好背道而馳<br />\n<br />\n政府一路做緊既野就係同我地鬥搶道德高地, 去污名化我地<br />\n<br />\n政府不斷用流氓用下三流手段去對待我地就係想我地失去理性<br />\n<br />\n想我地其中有人由天使同騎士墜落成惡魔, 學左共產黨果套做事方式, 呢條係不歸路黎<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山, 但唔代表爬到見唔到大家既影子, 始終都要齊上齊落, 大家要明白呢個道理</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>當然我都好希望所有F既人可以練功一齊升到E級以上</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"d95d4f9df2668cc6daee1c32d0cd69b9b64fcbf4","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1845c25231cc0d3b4480e5c7d401ef54f48cae4","tid":1475780,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNiV8GW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNiV8GW.jpg&h=106a82a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e047ea05b084a7cbc443c794ba2a3235a7bbdbd0","tid":1475780,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:17:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b29a3b63a6a15b03c21754c1c5a3ae44131e1dd3","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:18:45.000Z","msg":"我唔係叫大家做和理非<br />\n<br />\n我係叫大家一齊升級, 但唔好去到無底線就得"},{"pid":"2a47cdba77adbe085e611dc89912e7f2e948e193","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1845c25231cc0d3b4480e5c7d401ef54f48cae4","tid":1475780,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FNiV8GW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFNiV8GW.jpg&h=106a82a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:19:51.000Z","msg":"緊係車死下面喇.<br />\n<br />\n但做開車果個就另一回事"},{"pid":"e75e4e344a726f85e1244143a2fe3030025f3463","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76823e4172941bd75e39b6002b78454bf4b4fc98","tid":1475780,"uid":133903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"A、B都唔割！屌，對家黑警一早已經去到A、B級"},{"pid":"afdbdd7ca277882fddef98ec4da5eab1e5fec06a","tid":1475780,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"Warrior 戰士"},{"pid":"5a9d102817f222f65ffbebe34aceb80626c3be63","tid":1475780,"uid":19817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76823e4172941bd75e39b6002b78454bf4b4fc98","tid":1475780,"uid":133903,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:28:22.000Z","msg":"A、B都唔割！屌，對家黑警一早已經去到A、B級"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"唔係割定唔割,   去到烏克蘭咁樣緊係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n但難聽D講 香港未係住"},{"pid":"b7469cd35f5b78142ea76cfa9a21893314eb37e2","tid":1475780,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">NOW OR NEVER</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dYUik2W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdYUik2W.jpg&h=b7b2e1de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hrs0znW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHrs0znW.png&h=d1fc316e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xqMkznX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxqMkznX.jpg&h=c5dabcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hvEPWh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hvEPWh.jpg&h=f7d69869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEYbF2X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEYbF2X.jpg&h=f6523fdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9TAab9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht